commentary: LOLCAT. I've already talked about this. What is there left to even say. I make no excuses for my crimes. I think I just really wanted to make this joke and warped the entire concept of her land around this idea, which is why it's so stupid. So that's why Nepeta, one of the explicit whipping-kids of the story, gets arguably the dumbest land, just like another whipping-kid, Sollux, gets unarguably the most awful land. Someone needs to swoop in to save these children from my horrendous decisions.
